{"tid":162860,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得越係多人撐鬍鬚就越恐怖","createTime":"2017-03-19T14:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-19T15:46:07.000Z","uid":70429,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0385e2e48d61f08872a09b8e0ff3d604bb08005a","tid":162860,"uid":70429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:30:59.000Z","msg":"e+就好似黑白分明咁,<br />\n鬍鬚忠林鄭奸.<br />\n<br />\n但其實明明2個都係奸,<br />\n咁多年鬍鬚做財政司,貧富懸殊,樓價問題依然越來越嚴重.<br />\n只不過林鄭突登被突顯到係好撚奸.<br />\n襯托之下鬍鬚就顯得好少少咁.<br />\n跟住個個就走去支持鬍鬚,好似唔記得曬佢以前d功過咁.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家個fb同毒果都係鬍鬚派咁,<br />\n上一次仲話有梁唐5打5.<br />\n今次曾鄭9打1咁.<br />\n越係順利越係覺得恐怖.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人覺得好撚奇怪好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ccc7696193a9a52a53d9d6ddcfa8c4814b41fd","tid":162860,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:38:57.000Z","msg":"總覺得由選舉工程開始林鄭柒得太唔合理"},{"pid":"fb6f55ebf7fe773c8d159cc244a6096e1271d08e","tid":162860,"uid":70429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:39:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>總覺得由選舉工程開始林鄭柒得太唔合理</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係柒得好假<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7b62910ef3bad274254ba8a45f35c06a4cb0ae","tid":162860,"uid":37093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:50:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>總覺得由選舉工程開始林鄭柒得太唔合理</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係柒得好假<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似好刻意凸顯曾俊華嘅「貼地」，「勤力」，「聽民意」咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次林鄭柒完就有一大堆人吹奏薯片<br />\n分分鐘林鄭係中共推出嚟擋箭嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7c59e21ce37c85ed1260195965f4ec799bf709","tid":162860,"uid":4213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T14:52:33.000Z","msg":"邊個上都一樣<br />\n覺得薯片上會好果班<br />\n除左腦生癌智商低過40之外<br />\n無第啲原因"},{"pid":"092625f3bed38978120d27b91317bd37e8818240","